    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587540/extras/8739f7cc9c4130ea6d01dac095b393b2.avif?t=1768384380\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想过当个铁匠吗？在《铁匠铺传奇》里，不只是锤打铁砧那么简单。这里，你得打造的不仅仅是铁器，还有你自己的故事。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">设计梦想中的铁匠铺</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的铁匠铺完全由你来设计！无论是想要个酷炫的工作区，还是个舒适的休息角落，甚至是健身房或图书馆。还可以建造新的房间和地下设施，接受更加有挑战性的订单，让你的铁匠铺日益壮大！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">                      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587540/extras/cc302e87f9fadf7352ab601bba0327b1.poster.avif?t=1768384380\" width=500 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587540/extras/cc302e87f9fadf7352ab601bba0327b1.webm?t=1768384380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587540/extras/cc302e87f9fadf7352ab601bba0327b1.mp4?t=1768384380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">熔炉外的抉择</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在锻造之外，你将面临诸多抉择。你需要斡旋于相互冲突的各派系之间，和土匪交易可能会给你带来麻烦，但也可能意外收获；与贵族合作可能让你名声大噪。你决定履行的订单以及你对待每个派系的方式都会影响游戏世界，带来不同的结果。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">                      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587540/extras/ec223c3bd892e6556bf6a6ae67d3cf4e.poster.avif?t=1768384380\" width=500 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587540/extras/ec223c3bd892e6556bf6a6ae67d3cf4e.webm?t=1768384380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587540/extras/ec223c3bd892e6556bf6a6ae67d3cf4e.mp4?t=1768384380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">一段由破败到辉煌的旅程</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一名铁匠，处理订单是你的日常。可能是个简单的修理工作，也可能是为国王打造一件宝物。通过精心管理订单，提升你的声望等级，吸引贵族和名流。特别注意那些能带来丰厚回报的独特订单！比如为一位男爵的女儿打造独一无二的戒指，或为国王锻造传世之剑。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">                      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587540/extras/5d7781991479355cc145f28a1011bfef.poster.avif?t=1768384380\" width=500 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587540/extras/5d7781991479355cc145f28a1011bfef.webm?t=1768384380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587540/extras/5d7781991479355cc145f28a1011bfef.mp4?t=1768384380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">管理你的铁匠团队</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会遇到各种各样的工人。他们每个人都有自己的技能和性格。建设设施，安装便利设备，装饰房屋，创造一个愉快的工作环境。升级他们的工具，提高工作效率。通过为图书室添置新书，帮助员工提升技艺，让你的团队更快地帮你实现铁匠铺的梦想。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">                      <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587540/extras/a6a0b3032d6ccfd3fd8e7c0e55d7b7e9.poster.avif?t=1768384380\" width=500 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587540/extras/a6a0b3032d6ccfd3fd8e7c0e55d7b7e9.webm?t=1768384380\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1587540/extras/a6a0b3032d6ccfd3fd8e7c0e55d7b7e9.mp4?t=1768384380\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >那么，准备好开始你的铁匠生涯了吗？拿起你的锤子，一起来铸造属于你的传奇故事吧！</p>",
